list of tools I recommend
=========================

[ os ]
(desktop) archlabs: https://archlabslinux.com/
(phone) grapheneos: https://grapheneos.org/

[ window managers ]
dwm (C): https://dwm.suckless.org/
leftwm (rust): http://leftwm.org/

[ browsers ]
(desktop) qutebrowser: https://qutebrowser.org/
(phone) vanadium: https://github.com/GrapheneOS/Vanadium

[ email clients ]
neomutt: https://neomutt.org/
mailspring-libre: https://github.com/notpushkin/Mailspring-Libre

[ text editors ]
neovim: https://github.com/neovim/neovim
vscodium: https://vscodium.com/ 
wordgrinder: https://github.com/davidgiven/wordgrinder

[ private messingers ]
signal: https://www.signal.org/
briar: https://briarproject.org/

[ presentations ]
sent: http://tools.suckless.org/sent/
